# The `FoldingSetNodeWrapper` Class Template Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/foldingsetnodewrapper">FoldingSetNodeWrapper</a> - This template class is used to &quot;wrap&quot; arbitrary types in an enclosing object so that they can be inserted into FoldingSets. <a href="#details">More...</a>
